Each binary has a long pulse before it.

| Key | Binary |
| ---:| ---:|
| 1 | 1100000010000100 |
| 2 | 1100000001000100 |
| 3 | 1100000011000100 |
| 4 | 1100000000100100 |
| 5 | 1100000010100100 |
| 6 | 1100000001100100 |
| 7 | 1100000011100100 |
| 8 | 1100000000010100 |
| 9 | 1100000010010100 |
| 0 | 1100000000000100 |
| MUTE  | 1100000000111000 |
| LAST  | 1100000010100000 |
| Enter | 1100000011101110 |
| Delete| No Signal |
